# 🛡️ RBAC Portal — MERN Stack

A production-ready **Role-Based Access Control** portal with Google OAuth and JWT authentication.

---

## ✨ Features

- 🔐 **JWT Authentication** — Secure token-based auth with auto-refresh
- 🌐 **Google OAuth 2.0** — Sign In with Google via Passport.js
- 👥 **5 Role Tiers** — Super Admin → Admin → Manager → Editor → Viewer
- 🔒 **Granular Permissions** — 11 permission types, fully customizable per user
- 📊 **Admin Dashboard** — Stats, recent activity, role/permission map
- 👤 **User Management** — Full CRUD with pagination, search, and filters
- 🛡️ **Route Guards** — Protected routes by role and permission
- 🎨 **Premium Dark UI** — Sleek, production-grade interface

---

