## 🚀 Quick Start

### 1. Prerequisites
- Node.js v18+
- MongoDB (local or [MongoDB Atlas](https://cloud.mongodb.com))
- A Google Cloud project

### 2. Google OAuth Setup
1. Go to [Google Cloud Console](https://console.cloud.google.com)
2. Create a new project or select existing
3. Enable **Google+ API** or **Google Identity**
4. Go to **Credentials → Create → OAuth 2.0 Client ID**
5. Application type: **Web application**
6. Authorized redirect URIs: `http://localhost:5000/api/auth/google/callback`
7. Copy the **Client ID** and **Client Secret**

### 3. Backend Setup
```bash
cd backend
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your values:
#   MONGODB_URI, GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID, GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET, JWT_SECRET

npm install
npm run dev    # Starts on http://localhost:5000
```

### 4. Frontend Setup
```bash
cd frontend
cp .env.example .env
# .env should have: REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api

npm install
npm start      # Starts on http://localhost:3000
```

### 5. Create First Super Admin
After starting the backend, seed a super admin via Mongo shell or Compass:
```js
db.users.insertOne({
  name: "Super Admin",
  email: "admin@yourcompany.com",
  password: "$2a$12$...",  // bcrypt hash
  role: "super_admin",
  authProvider: "local",
  isActive: true,
  permissions: [
    "users:read","users:write","users:delete",
    "content:read","content:write","content:delete",
    "reports:read","reports:write",
    "settings:read","settings:write","analytics:read"
  ]
})
```
Or simply register via UI, then update the role in MongoDB:
```js
db.users.updateOne({ email: "you@email.com" }, { $set: { role: "super_admin" } })
```

---

## 🔑 Role Hierarchy

| Role | Level | Can Create Roles |
|------|-------|-----------------|
| `super_admin` | 5 | admin and below |
| `admin` | 4 | manager and below |
| `manager` | 3 | editor and below |
| `editor` | 2 | viewer only |
| `viewer` | 1 | none |

> **Rule:** A user can only assign roles strictly below their own.

---

## 🔒 Permissions Reference

| Permission | Description |
|-----------|-------------|
| `users:read` | View user list |
| `users:write` | Create/edit users |
| `users:delete` | Delete users |
| `content:read/write/delete` | Content management |
| `reports:read/write` | Reporting |
| `settings:read/write` | App settings |
| `analytics:read` | View analytics |

---

## 🛡️ API Endpoints

### Auth
| Method | Endpoint | Access |
|--------|----------|--------|
| POST | `/api/auth/register` | Public |
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | Public |
| GET | `/api/auth/google` | Public |
| GET | `/api/auth/google/callback` | OAuth |
| GET | `/api/auth/me` | Authenticated |
| POST | `/api/auth/logout` | Public |

### Users (self)
| Method | Endpoint | Access |
|--------|----------|--------|
| GET | `/api/users/profile` | Authenticated |
| PUT | `/api/users/profile` | Authenticated |
| PUT | `/api/users/change-password` | Authenticated |

### Admin
| Method | Endpoint | Access |
|--------|----------|--------|
| GET | `/api/admin/stats` | Admin+ |
| GET | `/api/admin/users` | Admin + users:read |
| POST | `/api/admin/users` | Admin + users:write |
| PUT | `/api/admin/users/:id` | Admin + users:write |
| DELETE | `/api/admin/users/:id` | Super Admin only |

